EXTRACTED VALUE: But it wasn't a holy man I found in the kitchen covered in pixy children, it was Glenn.
"With some help from Dellius, yes. Steward, clear the room!" Antony bellowed. "Where's Lucilius? I need Lucilius!"
I waited. In the seven years I'd worked for him, the lab director had never called me at three in the morning.
"You know the things you teach, Dad? Those are the same things that go into the training of a Jedi Knight."
